  <h2 id="what-is-machining-coolant">What is Machining Coolant?</h2>

  <div class="not-prose flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 items-start my-6">
    <div class="md:w-1/3 flex-shrink-0">
      <img
        src="/images/machining-coolant-recovery-centrifuge/Alfa-Laval-Industrial-Centrifuge-Coolant-1000.webp"
